fields.name: A Wonderful World
fields.description: In this satire from director Luis Estrada, a homeless man looking for a place to rest his weary head finds his life transformed when his window-ledge nap is mistaken for a suicide attempt.

fields.name: Ballot
fields.description: A teacher puts her life on the line to protect a ballot box full of crucial votes as corrupt forces threaten to overturn a key local election.

fields.name: Dr. Seuss' The Grinch
fields.description: A grump with a mean streak plots to bring Christmas to a halt in the cheerful town of Whoville. But a generous little girl could change his heart.
